title: Frenemies #1 - Trisha's New Boyfriend Is Hila's Brother
description: Welcome to episode #1 of our new venture- Frenemies, a podcast hosted by Ethan Klein and Trisha Paytas. Together Ethan and Trisha discuss her budding romance with Hila's brother Moses, STDs, OnlyFans, insane stalkers, and a whole lot more!
